### List n8n Workflows
GET http://omni-n8n:5678/api/v1/workflows
X-N8N-API-KEY: {{n8n_api_key}}

### Create Automation via MCP
POST http://omni-mcp-automation:8337/tools/create_automation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Every morning at 8 AM, check all service health via Orchestrator API, and if any critical service is unhealthy, send a summary to Mattermost #alerts and trigger an Omi haptic alert",
  "name": "Morning Health Check",
  "activate": true
}

### Audit Log — Recent Events
GET http://omni-audit-logger:9550/events?limit=50&event_type=pipeline.task_completed

### Audit Log — Resource Timeline
GET http://omni-audit-logger:9550/events/timeline/task/{{task_id}}
